<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Crocodile" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Crocodile,</orth> the animal Crocodilus: <cit><quote>the mournful c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.226" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 226</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>eat a c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.299" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 299</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>each drop she falls would prove a c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.257" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 1, 257</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 7, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 7, 31</bibl> <cit><quote>the tears of it are wet,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 7, 31</bibl></cit>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>